@startuml seq-submission-judge
hide footbox
scale max 1500 width
scale max 2200 height
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title 代码提交与判题（异步全链路）

actor "普通用户" as Client
participant "SubmissionController" as Ctl
participant "SubmissionService" as SubSvc
participant "SubmissionMapper" as SubMapper
participant "ProblemService" as ProbSvc
participant "JudgeService" as JudgeSvc
participant "TestCaseService" as TcSvc
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "JudgeRequestListener" as JReq
participant "Envoy 判题服务" as Envoy
participant "JudgeResultListener" as JRes
participant "SubmissionWebSocketHandler" as WS
database "MySQL" as DB

note over Client, Ctl : JWT 鉴权；管理员角色禁止提交

== 提交阶段（同步） ==

Client -> WS : WebSocket 连接 /ws/submission/{submissionId}
Client -> Ctl : POST /api/submission\n(code, language, problemId)

Ctl -> SubSvc : submit(...)
SubSvc -> SubMapper : insert submission\nstatus = waiting
SubMapper -> DB : INSERT
DB --> SubSvc : submissionId
SubSvc -> ProbSvc : invalidateProblemDetailCaches
SubSvc -> JudgeSvc : judge(problemId, code, language, id)

JudgeSvc -> TcSvc : getTestCaseListByProblemId
TcSvc -> DB : SELECT test_cases
JudgeSvc -> MQ : 发布 JudgeRequest
JudgeSvc --> SubSvc : void
SubSvc --> Ctl : submissionId
Ctl --> Client : 200 返回提交 id

== 判题阶段（异步） ==

MQ -> JReq : 消费判题请求
JReq -> Envoy : POST /judge
Envoy --> JReq : JudgeResponse

alt 判题服务异常
  JReq -> MQ : 发布错误 Verdict
else 判题成功
  JReq -> MQ : 发布 JudgeResponse
end

MQ -> JRes : 消费判题结果
JRes -> SubSvc : update(JudgeResult, submissionId)
SubSvc -> SubMapper : UPDATE status, time, memory
SubMapper -> DB : UPDATE
JRes -> WS : pushJudgeResult(submissionId, result)
WS --> Client : WebSocket 推送判题结果

@enduml
